Package org.apache.velocity.runtime.visitor

Class BaseVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.velocity.runtime.visitor.BaseVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
StandardParserVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
NodeViewMode
public abstract class BaseVisitor extends Object implements StandardParserVisitor
This is the base class for all visitors. For each AST node, this class will provide a bare-bones method for traversal.
Version:
$Id$
Author:
Jason van Zyl, Geir Magnusson Jr.
